            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Hd1e108">Rubrica 3</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De conscientia benignitatis et malignitatis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e114">
                De conscientia benignitatis 
                et malignitatis Rubrica 3
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e121">
                <cb ed="#K" n="b"/>
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref>Oratius epistolarum li i e i</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e127">Hic murus eneus extat 
              <lb ed="#K"/>Nil conscii sibi nulla pal<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>lescere 
              culpa</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e134">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref>Tullius de senectute</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e138">Conscientia bene acte 
              <lb ed="#K"/>vite multorumque beneficiorum re<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>cordatio 
              iocundissima est</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e147"> 
              <ref>Idem 
              <lb ed="#K"/>tuscalanarum questionum li 2</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e149">Nullum thea<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>trum 
              virtute et conscientia maius est</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e157">
              <lb ed="#K"/> <ref>Quidius de fastis li i</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e161">Conscientia 
              <lb ed="#K"/>mens vt cuique sua est sic con<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>cipit 
              intra Pectore profecto spem<lb ed="#K" break="no"/>que 
              metumque suo</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e169"> 
              <ref>Lib 4</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e171">Conscia 
              <lb ed="#K"/>mens recti fame mendacia 
              <lb ed="#K"/>ridet
        Sed nos in vitium credula turba sumus.</quote>
         <ref> Seneca in prouerb.</ref> <quote>Plerique famam: conscien
        tiam pauci verentur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e183">
               
                <ref> Paulus apostolus epistola. 2. ad corinth. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e187">Gloria
        nostra hoc est testimonium conscientie nostre.</quote>
        <ref> Statius thebandos li. 2.</ref> <quote>O sper timidum scelus</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e195">
               
                <ref> Iuuenalis li. 2. satis i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e199">Cui frigida mens est
        Criminibus tacita sudant praecordia culpa.</quote>
         <ref> Marcialis cocus li. vndique suscepto. c. 6.</ref>
         <quote>Ibis ad occultos tramites loca deuia mundi
        Peccatum tecum est: conscientie culpa comes.
        Alterius censor: censor et esto tuus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e213">
               
                <ref> Ambrosius de officiis li. 2. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e217">Uitam bea
        tam efficiunt tranquillitas conscientie et se
        curitas innocentie. <!--79.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="26-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e232">
               
                <ref> Augustinus in epig. prospe. 8. emp.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e236">Bo
        na conscientia tranquillum facit animu.</quote>
         <ref>Macrobius de somno scipionis li. 2. et fi.</ref>
         <quote>Uirtutis fructum sapiens in conscientia ponit:
        minus perfctus in gloria.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e248">
               
                <ref> Cato. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e252">Conscius ipse sibi: de se putat
        omnia dici.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e258">
               
                <ref> Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 7. c. 32.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e262">Totum vi
        tiosum geritur vbi conscientie puritas non ha
        betur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e270"> <ref> Li. 8. e. 18.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e272">Sicut conscientia leta est
        que prouehitur meritis: ita sub reatu iacet
        qui se imparem cognoscit muneribus conse
        cutis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e282"> <ref> Libro. 11. c. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e284">Quid acquiri puta
        tur vbi conscientia bona perditur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e290">
               
                <ref> Isidorus soliloquiorum li. 2. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e294">Deus con
        scientias iudicat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e301"> <ref> c. 37.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e303">Etsi non te damnet
        publica fama: condennat propria conscia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e309"> <ref> c. 38</ref>
         <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e311">Conscientia rei semper tin pena est. Mens
        male conscientie propriis agitatur stimulis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e319">
               
                <ref> Prouerb. vulgar.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e323">Lamore guasta la conscia</quote>
            </p>
